text: Cunter was a municipality in the district of Albula in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. On 1 January 2016, the former municipalities of Cunter, Bivio, Marmorera, Mulegns, Riom-Parsonz, Salouf, Savognin, Sur and Tinizong-Rona merged into the new municipality of Surses.
